%N A394922 Decimal expansion of the probability that a straight line drawn through a point uniformly selected at random in the interior of a cube, with a direction independently and uniformly selected at random, intersects two opposite faces.
%F A394922 Equals (6/Pi) * (2*sqrt(2) - sqrt(3) - 1 - 2 * log((2 + sqrt(2))/(1 + sqrt(3)))) + 1.
%F A394922 Equals (6/Pi) * (2*sqrt(2) - sqrt(3) - 1 + arccosh(2) - 2 * arcsinh(1)) + 1.
%F A394922 Equals (6/Pi) * (2*sqrt(2) - sqrt(3) - 1 + arctanh(sqrt(3)) + arctanh(1/sqrt(3)) - arctanh(sqrt(2)) - arcsinh(1)) + 1.
%F A394922 Equals (6/Pi) * (2*sqrt(2) - sqrt(3) - 1 - asinh(5 / sqrt(59 + 24 * sqrt(6)))) + 1.
%F A394922 Equals (6/Pi) * Integral_{x,y=0..1} arctan(x*y/sqrt(1 + x^2 + y^2)).
%F A394922 Equals (6/Pi) * Integral_{x,y=0..1} (1-x)*(1-y)/(1 + x^2 + y^2)^(3/2).
%F A394922 Equals 3 * A394921.
%e A394922 0.3326704029479557283589843223397228396571405224211102...
%t A394922 RealDigits[6/Pi * (2 * Sqrt[2] - Sqrt[3] - 1 - 2 * Log[(2 + Sqrt[2])/(1 + Sqrt[3])]) + 1, 10, 120][[1]]
%o A394922 (PARI) (6/Pi) * (2*sqrt(2) - sqrt(3) - 1 - 2 * log((2 + sqrt(2))/(1 + sqrt(3)))) + 1
